rue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iri1665702586413.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iri1665702586413.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iri1665702586413.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iri1665702586413\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Is Static\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the field contents are same for all occurrences of the entity.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iri1665702586413__section_w2909ab1b5b1_w2910ab1b5_w2911ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__2\">\n Property value is inherited.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code> (Bound to entity) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__2\">The field's value and properties are shared by\n                        all occurrences, so the content is the same. <p class=\"p\">The value can be changed in\n                           script, but not by the user. Properties can be changed using\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"iri1665702586413__note_w2912ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3b3_w2913ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3_w2914ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3_w2915ab1b5b1b1b3b7_w2916ab1b5b1b1b3_w2917ab1b5b1b1_w2918ab1b5b1_w2919ab1b5_w2920ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The widget associated with the field is associated with the\n                           occurrence, not the entity. If you use\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>, only the properties in the\n                           current occurrence are changed.</div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"iri1665702586413__note_w2921ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3b5_w2922ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3b3_w2923ab1b5b1b1b3b7b3_w2924ab1b5b1b1b3b7_w2925ab1b5b1b1b3_w2926ab1b5b1b1_w2927ab1b5b1_w2928ab1b5_w2929ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The value is not cleared by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span>\n                           ProcScript statement.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">F</code> (Bound to occurrence) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iri1665702586413__table_d11492e1_d11493e1_d11494e1__entry__2\">\n The field's value and properties can be addressed and manipulated at the occurrence level, so they can have different values in every occurrence.\n <p class=\"p\">The field's properties can be manipulated using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iri1665702586413__section_ojk_rks_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497640e145\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iri1665702586413__p_d99233e1_d99234e1_d99235e1\">This property can only be set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n            for non-database fields that cannot be externalized (<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is External</span>\n            is <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code>) .</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iri1665702586413__p_d99236e1_d99237e1_d99238e1\">In the vast majority of cases, a field is not static.\n            Each occurrence of the entity in the component contains an occurrence of the field, and\n            it can be changed and manipulated only in that occurrence, without affecting field in\n            other occurrences.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iri1665702586413__p_d99239e1_d99240e1_d99241e1\">However, it is sometimes useful to have a field\n            display the same content in all occurrences of the entity. For example, you might want\n            to display an icon on each record. In this case, set <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is Static</span> to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>. When you can change the value the field, the change is applied\n            to all occurrences of the entity.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iri1665702586413__section_aps_sks_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497640e175\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"iri1665702586413__ul_lpq_tks_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iri1665702586413__li_d39908e1_d39909e1_d39910e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Is External</a><p>Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613775\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Is Static Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Is Static Determines whether the field contents are same for all occurrences of the entity. Value Description \"\" Property value is inherited. T (Bound to entity) The field's value and properties are shared by all occurrences, so the content is the same. The value can be changed in script, but not by the user. Properties can be changed using $properties . Note: The widget associated with the field is associated with the occurrence, not the entity. If you use $fieldproperties , only the properties in the current occurrence are changed. Note: The value is not cleared by the clear ProcScript statement. F (Bound to occurrence) The field's value and properties can be addressed and manipulated at the occurrence level, so they can have different values in every occurrence. The field's properties can be manipulated using $fieldproperties . Description This property can only be set to True for non-database fields that cannot be externalized ( Is External is F ) . In the vast majority of cases, a field is not static. Each occurrence of the entity in the component contains an occurrence of the field, and it can be changed and manipulated only in that occurrence, without affecting field in other occurrences. However, it is sometimes useful to have a field display the same content in all occurrences of the entity. For example, you might want to display an icon on each record. In this case, set Is Static to True . When you can change the value the field, the change is applied to all occurrences of the entity. Applies To Field Related Links Is External Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}